WEBVTT

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:30.696
(Laughter)

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:32.936
So I would argue
we're still in the process

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:34.816
of exhausting every other possibility,

00:06:34.840 --> 00:06:37.416
but I do think we will prevail.

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:38.896
But I need your help.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.176
This is my ask.

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:43.656
I ask not that you take
your recycling out on Wednesday,

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:46.656
but that you engage
with every business leader,

00:06:46.680 --> 00:06:49.496
every technology leader,
every government leader,

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:52.096
and ask them, "Ma'am, sir,

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:54.800
what are you doing
to stabilize the climate?"

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:57.056
It's just that simple.

00:06:57.080 --> 00:07:00.576
Because when enough people care enough,